title: Sarh — Data-flow Context diagram (DFD Level 0 / Single process)
---
flowchart LR
    classDef ext   fill:#bae6fd,stroke:#0284c7,color:#0c4a6e
    classDef sarh  fill:#0F172A,stroke:#000,color:#F97316,rx:80,ry:80
    classDef svc   fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#f59e0b,color:#78350f

    Citizen[Citizen]:::ext
    Officer[Registry officer]:::ext
    Manager[Department manager]:::ext

    SARH(((Sarh Platform))):::sarh

    SSI[SSI Provider]:::svc
    MAP[Map Service API]:::svc
    NOTIF[Notification Service]:::svc
    NFT[NFT Minting Service<br/>Smart Contract]:::svc

    Citizen -->|"Land docs + GPS coords"| SARH
    SARH -->|"Profile + identity info"| Citizen
    SARH -->|"Notifications + application status"| Citizen
    SARH -->|"Deed PDF + NFT token URI"| Citizen

    Officer -->|"Map verification + report"| SARH
    SARH -->|"Requests for review"| Officer

    Manager -->|"Approval response"| SARH
    SARH -->|"Approval requests + decree drafts"| Manager

    SARH -->|"Request identity verification"| SSI
    SSI -->|"Verifiable credential result"| SARH

    SARH -->|"Coordinates + boundary check"| MAP
    MAP -->|"Spatial validation result"| SARH

    SARH -->|"Notification content + user contact"| NOTIF
    NOTIF -->|"Delivery status"| SARH

    SARH -->|"Property metadata + owner DID"| NFT
    NFT -->|"Token id + tx hash + minting confirmation"| SARH
